        "faq_1": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What is a Brand Partner?",
            "answer": "A Brand Partner is someone who joins Yoli not just as a customer, but as a business builder. As a Brand Partner, you get wholesale pricing on all products, access to exclusive promotions, and the opportunity to earn income by sharing Yoli with others. You'll receive your own personalized website, marketing tools, and mentorship from experienced partners to help you grow."
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do Brand Partners share Yoli?",
            "answer": "Sharing Yoli is simple and personal. Brand Partners share their favorite products through conversations with friends and family, social media, and their personalized Yoli website. When someone you recommend places an order, you earn credit. There's no pressure to sell—just authentic recommendations about products you love. Yoli provides all the tools, training, and support you need to share effectively."
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I join just for the discounts?",
            "answer": "Absolutely! Many people join Yoli simply to enjoy wholesale pricing on products they love. As a member, you'll get significant savings on all Yoli products without any requirement to build a business or share with others. You can simply enjoy the products at the best possible price and upgrade to Brand Partner status anytime if you decide you want to start earning."
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What's included in the Launch Pack vs. Transformation Path Pack?",
            "answer": "The <strong>Launch Pack</strong> is perfect for those starting their wellness journey. Choose between Vital Omegas+ or Vital Balance, mix and match your favorites, and get our most essential products. It comes in three sizes—Launch, Builder, and Pro Builder—so you can pick what fits your goals.<br><br>The <strong>Transformation Path Pack</strong> is our complete wellness experience. It includes Yoli's best products and resources for your best self, including the Basics Plus Transformation kit. This is ideal for those ready to fully embrace the Yoli lifestyle and see maximum results."
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "faq_item",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I earn rewards and bonuses?",
            "answer": "Yoli offers multiple ways to earn! When your customers place orders, you receive commission on those sales. Enroll new Partners with Transformation Kits and earn bonuses—like $200 for enrolling just 2 Partners in your first week. Sign up customers with kits for additional bonuses, plus earn free Yoli products worth $200. Hit Star Rank in Week 1 for an extra $100 bonus. As you grow, you can qualify for travel incentives and even the Yoli luxury car program!"
          }
        }
      }
